snippet.title: Announcing "P.E with Joe" | Daily LIVE workouts for kids | The Body Coach
snippet.description:
Starting Monday 23rd March I'm going to be hosting a free workout aimed at kids LIVE on my YouTube channel.

With the schools closed and with us all spending more time at home, it's more important than ever that we keep moving and stay healthy and positive.

Exercise is an amazing tool to help us feel happier, more energised, and more optimistic.  

The workouts will be fun and suitable for all ages and even the adults can get involved. 

You don't need any equipment, so just tune in to my YouTube channel at 9am each morning for a 30-minute, fun workout. 

One more thing! I really need your help to spread this message. So please please share this with everyone that might like to get involved, and together we can help keep the nation moving 🙏🏻

Lots of love, Joe x

snippet.title: CRISTIANO RONALDO KIDS workout at home! HIIT fitness class! Fun with Dimi #stayhome
snippet.description:
Cristiano Ronaldo's home workout routine inspired Dimi to recreate a kids workout routine. During quarantine it is important for kids and their families to stay active, strong and positive and who better to influence a short kids or family workout than Ronaldo!

This is a fun workout with 7 exercises that can be done at home or any where else.  The workout routine is a full-body routine that includes legs, abs, chest, glutes, strength and agility. It is structured in a HIIT workout format with 30 seconds high intensity training and 30 seconds rest. Dimi shows and explains each exercise and then together you can follow along to each exercise for 30 seconds.

This is a fun workout for kids to follow along too or to do as a family!
